title: Stan Getz - Getz Plays Jobim: The Girl From Ipanema
description:
Finally, on one CD, every Antonio Carlos Jobim Song Stan Getz recorded for Verve.

The great sensitivity shown by Getz for this material, and the adventurousness of Jobim were a match made in heaven.

Essential.
